    }

    HttpTask --> ApiSecurity : 3. Esp Now Key is for security
    ApiSecurity --> SlaveTask : 4. Handle Esp Now key
    SlaveTask --> EspNowTask : 5. Send to other nodes (for all nodes)
    EspNowTask ..> SlaveTask: 5b Ack
    SlaveTask --> NvsTask : 6. Store in NVS 
    NvsTask ..> SlaveTask : 6b. Ack
    SlaveTask --> HttpTask : 7. Respond to HTTP request


}

DmxControllerWebserverSlave --|> SlaveTask
DmxControllerHttpTask --> HttpTask : 2. (Common API)
PresetsTask --|> RtosTask

